{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Assessment Engine API",
    "description": "<h2>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assessment/Survey Management</li>\n  <li>User Responses to Assessment</li>\n  <li>User's Assessment Profile</li>\n</ul>\n<p> The Assessment Engine provides a way to collect user responses to assessments/surveys. It supports assessments created using <b><a target=\"_blank\" href=https://surveyjs.io/create-survey>surveyjs</a></b>. The Assessment Engine works with <b><a target=\"_blank\" href=https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis/mimik/Survey>Survey</a></b> service to manage list of available surveys. The service also maintains the latest values retrieved from user responses accross all the assessment answered by the user, what we call user's assessment profile.\n</p>\n",
    "contact": {
      "name": "mimik technology inc.",
      "url": "https://developer.mimik.com",
      "email": "support@mimik.com"
    },
    "license": {
      "name": "Apache 2.0",
      "url": "http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html"
    },
    "version": "2.0.2",
    "x-jentic-source-url": "https://api.swaggerhub.com/apis/mimik/Assessment/2.0.2/swagger.json"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "/assessmentEngine/v1"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "description": "Admin user calls"
    },
    {
      "name": "System",
      "description": "Server to server calls"
    },
    {
      "name": "User",
      "description": "User calls"
    }
